
Manual preparation - steps:

1) Generate certificates (CA, certs for centralpoint and each vrouter).
2) Modify the configuration file for the OpenVPN server (directory files/centralpoint/ccd).
3) Modify the configuration file for vRouters (directory files/client/).
4) Modify the ansible's host file (file ansible-scripts/hosts)
5) Start ansible playbook in ansible-scripts directory: ansible-playbook -i hosts install.yml
	

